{
  "stem": "13690.3",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 10.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We were decided that we will go to the hiding place, to that village where my other relatives are.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So going there, we did not know exactly how to go.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Mr.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Placzek, the man who was hiding us, dressed up himself in his honorary uniform.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "He was from the honorary [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] fire department, and he put out his uniform.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And so to say, that he is-- in case if he's being checked or being asked any questions, that he could identify himself.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So he took us around that city to cross the river.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And he said he would take us all the way.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We kept on saying, 'It's not needed.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It's not necessary.' But he kept on insisting that he wants to see us on the other side of the town.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "While we reached that river-- that river that I remember I used to play always, jumping back and forth-- that river, it was a rain probably a few days before, a week before.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "That river was quite deep.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And it became a little bit wider, as I remember.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Everybody could cross it.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "My mother, may she rest in peace, couldn't do it.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I was wearing-- it was summer months, but I was wearing high boots.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Why did I wear boots?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It's all so silly.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I had, in the boots, built in some golden coins.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So I did not want to give up the golden coins.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The boots were small.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The boots were made two years ago.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So I grew in the two years, if not that much.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "The boots, I can hardly fit in, bu I got in.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So finally, when I had to cross that river, and I had to carry my mother, I said, 'Look, I have boots.",
      "word_count": 22
    }
  ],
